      "type": "content-list",
      "blocks": {
        "image_WfARFa": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "apply_overlay": false,
            "devices": "mobile_desktop",
            "content_position": "underLeft",
            "subheading": "",
            "title": "<p>The Celebration Doesn't End When The Music Does</p>",
            "description": "<p>The most thoughtful wedding details are often the ones that continue to hold meaning long after the day itself. Whether it's a keepsake your guests take home or something that becomes part of your everyday life together, these small touches allow your celebration to live on.</p><p>For Elsa, guests took home custom matchboxes as a simple keepsake, a small reminder of the celebration designed to find a place in their homes long after the last dance.</p><p>Rather than a traditional guest book, the couple invited guests to sign a framed vinyl record of their first dance song. Today, it hangs in the hallway of their home, transforming a beautiful memory into something they pass each day.</p><p></p>",
            "description_mobile": "<p>The most thoughtful wedding details are often the ones that continue to hold meaning long after the day itself. Whether it's a keepsake your guests take home or something that becomes part of your everyday life together, these small touches allow your celebration to live on.</p><p>For Elsa, guests took home custom matchboxes as a simple keepsake, a small reminder of the celebration designed to find a place in their homes long after the last dance.</p><p>Rather than a traditional guest book, the couple invited guests to sign a framed vinyl record of their first dance song. Today, it hangs in the hallway of their home, transforming a beautiful memory into something they pass each day.</p>",
            "colour_style": "dark",
